name: cult.ure 01 - Blood Wallet
description:
We were born into a perverted, faux reality. Our minds were not developed naturally but rather artificially.

Its not personal, it's just business.

Those who control the Power-of-Perception also control Deception-for-Profit: Menticide.

As Menticide has created a false reality, what we think is good and right could very well be completely false and destructive.

Who are we now and how far away are we from our truly natural selves?
